com.b2international.snowowl.core.api

Interface IStatement<K>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - - type parameter of the key (this is the unique identifier).
    All Superinterfaces:
    IComponent<K>, IdProvider<K>, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SnomedRelationshipIndexEntry

    public interface IStatement<K>
extends IComponent<K>
    Represents a terminology independent statement with an object (source), an attribute (type) and a value (destination) ID.

    The following features are supported:

    • Retrieve the source concept ID.
    • Retrieve the type conceptID.
    • Retrieve the destination concept ID.
